@startuml
title UC05 - Prediction State
[*] --> NotPredicted
NotPredicted --> Draft : select criteria
Draft --> Submitted : submit before deadline
Submitted --> Edited : edit before deadline
Edited --> Submitted : save
Submitted --> Locked : deadline or match starts
Locked --> Scored : official result finished
Locked --> Cancelled : match cancelled
Scored --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]
@enduml
